Name: Krom
Review Text: Cafe Krom is an original Dutch pub.  In Dutch, they call this a type of cafe "Brown cafe."  Why?  First, it literally has to do with the interior color: the pub is dark brown.  The bar is made of dark brown wood, and it is dark inside the ‚Ä¶

Name: Krom
Review Text: Good prices, very good prices to be Amsterdam. A large selection of beers and drinks. The Juke box is a nice touch, terrace available, highly recommended!

Name: Krom
Review Text: Nice, attentive bar staff.  Busy pub, seemingly full of mostly locals. Good beer selection and snacks (bitterballen was yummy). Old school juke box was a nice touch in this cozy corner pub with a nice outdoor patio as well.

Name: Krom
